Title: An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Tominobo Proper in Iligan City to Barangay Tomas L. Cabili
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 196
An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Tominobo Proper in Iligan City to Barangay Tomas L. Cabili
Section 1. The name of Barangay Tominobo Proper in Iligan City is hereby changed to Barangay Tomas L. Cabili.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 16, 1982
